'''雅克·伊隆達·马霍马'''（{{lang-fr|'''Jacques Ilonda Maghoma'''}}，{{bd|1987年|10月23日|catIdx=Maghoa, Jacques}}）是一名[[剛果民主共和國|剛果]]籍[[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[中場_(足球)|中場]]，現效力於[[印度足球甲级联赛|印度足球甲级联赛]]球會[[东孟加拉足球俱乐部|東賓高]]。

==球會生涯==
===热刺===
马霍马生於[[薩伊|薩伊]][[盧本巴希|盧本巴希]]，在2003年加入熱刺青訓系統，後來晉升至預備隊並有不少上陣紀錄。2009年6月，在熱刺學師五年後終被球會放棄<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tottenhamhotspur.com/news/articles/playerupdate010609.html|title=Player Update|publisher=Tottenham Hotspur F.C.|date=13 June 2015|accessdate=1 June 2009|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090605064158/http://www.tottenhamhotspur.com/news/articles/playerupdate010609.html|archivedate=2009-06-05|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

===保顿艾尔宾===
自由身的马霍马在保顿艾尔宾<ref>{{cite news|title=Brewers keen on Maghoma|url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11750/5433121/brewers-keen-on-Maghoma|publisher=Sky Sports|date=14 July 2009|accessdate=13 June 2015|archive-date=2020-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200718210423/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11750/5433121/brewers-keen-on-maghoma|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[靴尔福特联足球俱乐部|靴尔福特联]]短暫試訓後，他決定與[[保顿艾尔宾足球俱乐部|保顿艾尔宾]]簽約兩年<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11771_5436644,00.html |title=Burton bring in Maghoma. |date=16 July 2009 |accessdate=9 August 2009 |publisher=Sky Sports |archive-date=2016-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160415041928/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11771_5436644,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2009年8月8日，马霍马首次上場作客對戰[[谢斯伯利足球俱乐部|谢斯伯利]]，以3-1落敗<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_3/8187499.stm |title=Shrewsbury 3–1 Burton Albion |date=8 August 2009 |publisher=BBC Sport |accessdate=30 August 2015 |archive-date=2020-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200328103542/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_3/8187499.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他首顆職業進球是10月19日以2-0擊敗[[巴尼特足球俱乐部|巴尼特]]的比賽<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/8295679.stm |title=Burton 2–0 Barnet |publisher=BBC Sport |date=19 October 2009 |accessdate=27 June 2013 |archive-date=2019-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190728053808/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/8295679.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，第二顆進球是2010年2月6日主場以1-0戰勝[[韦尔港足球俱乐部|韦尔港]]<ref>{{cite news |title=Burton Albion 1–0 Port Vale |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_3/8503210.stm|publisher=BBC Sport|date=6 February 2010|accessdate=13 June 2015}}</ref>，2月16日作客[[摩尔甘比足球俱乐部|摩尔甘比]]再進一球，球隊最終以3-2落敗<ref>{{cite news|title=Morecambe 3–2 Burton Albion|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_3/8494407.stm|publisher=BBC Sport|date=16 February 2010|accessdate=13 June 2015}}</ref>。在對[[切尔滕汉姆足球俱乐部|切尔滕汉姆]]的比賽，马霍马弄傷了膝部<ref>{{cite news|title=Webster remains in contention|url=http://www.burtonmail.co.uk/Webster-remains-contention/story-21530172-detail/story.html|newspaper=Burton Mail|date=17 March 2010|accessdate=13 June 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923222047/http://www.burtonmail.co.uk/Webster-remains-contention/story-21530172-detail/story.html|archivedate=2015年9月23日}}</ref>，至4月5日對[[貝里足球俱樂部|貝里]]的比賽才能康復上場<ref>{{cite news|title=Bury 3–0 Burton Albion|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_3/8598703.stm|publisher=BBC Sport|date=5 April 2010|accessdate=13 June 2015}}</ref>。可是對[[伯恩茅斯足球俱乐部|伯恩茅斯]]的比賽再次弄傷膝部，這次需要開刀做手術，缺席賽季餘下兩場賽事<ref>{{cite news|title=Maghoma's season is ended by injury|url=http://www.burtonmail.co.uk/Maghomas-season-ended-injury/story-21534142-detail/story.html|publisher=Burton Mail|date=29 April 2010|accessdate=13 June 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150614091533/http://www.burtonmail.co.uk/Maghomas-season-ended-injury/story-21534142-detail/story.html|archivedate=2015年6月14日}}</ref>。马霍马首個職業賽季在各項比賽共上場38次及打3進球。

马霍马在2010/11季前熱身賽對[[伊爾基斯頓足球會|伊爾基斯頓]]的賽事重返球場<ref>{{cite news|title=Peschisolido hails hotshot trialists|url=http://www.burtonmail.co.uk/Peschisolido-hails-hotshot-trialists/story-21534252-detail/story.html|newspaper=Burton Mail|date=12 July 2010|accessdate=13 June 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150614081125/http://www.burtonmail.co.uk/Peschisolido-hails-hotshot-trialists/story-21534252-detail/story.html|archivedate=2015年6月14日}}</ref>，他在9月初拒絕國家隊的徵召以集中精力在球隊賽事上<ref>{{cite news|title=Maghoma's international ambitions are set aside|url=http://www.burtonmail.co.uk/Maghomas-international-ambitions-set-aside/story-21534298-detail/story.html|publisher=Burton Mail|date=3 September 2010|accessdate=13 June 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150614081636/http://www.burtonmail.co.uk/Maghomas-international-ambitions-set-aside/story-21534298-detail/story.html|archivedate=2015年6月14日}}</ref> ，並在2010年9月18日對[[克鲁足球俱乐部|克鲁]]的賽事打進新賽季首顆進球，以1-1戰平<ref>{{cite news|title=Burton Albion 1–1 Crewe Alexandra |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_3/8989357.stm|publisher=BBC Sport|date=18 September 2010|accessdate=13 June 2015}}</ref>。其後在[[英格蘭足總盃|足總盃]]第二輪以3-1擊敗[[切斯特菲尔德足球俱乐部|切斯特菲尔德]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Burton Albion 3–1 Chesterfield|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/fa_cup/9206708.stm|publisher=BBC Sport|date=27 November 2010|accessdate=13 June 2015}}</ref>和3-1聯賽戰勝[[绍森德足球俱乐部|绍森德]]的賽事均取得進球<ref>{{cite news|title=Burton Albion 3–1 Southend United|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_3/9254994.stm|publisher=BBC Sport|date=11 December 2010|accessdate=13 June 2015}}</ref>。之後對摩尔甘比<ref>{{cite news|title=Morecambe 2–1 Burton Albion|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_3/12945294.stm|publisher=BBC Sport|date=9 April 2015|accessdate=13 June 2015}}</ref> 和切尔滕汉姆的比賽他亦取得進球<ref>{{cite news|title=Burton Albion 2–0 Cheltenham Town|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_3/13022958.stm|publisher=BBC Sport|date=16 April 2011|accessdate=13 June 2015}}</ref>。在1-1戰平绍森德的賽事，马霍马在完場前6分鐘因為向绍森德球迷使用侵犯性語言而領紅，而此比賽結果亦使球隊保級成功<ref>{{cite news|title=Southend United 1–1 Burton Albion|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_3/13174493.stm|publisher=BBC Sport|date=30 April 2011|accessdate=13 June 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Malone to ponder future after goalscoring show|url=http://www.burtonmail.co.uk/Malone-ponder-future-goalscoring/story-21534556-detail/story.html|newspaper=Burton Mail|date=2 May 2011|accessdate=13 June 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150614081356/http://www.burtonmail.co.uk/Malone-ponder-future-goalscoring/story-21534556-detail/story.html|archivedate=2015年6月14日}}</ref>。马霍马成為球隊最穩定的外場球員，賽季共上場45次打入5球<ref>{{cite news|title=Brewers all set for a Legz show at awards night|url=http://www.burtonmail.co.uk/Brewers-set-Legz-awards-night/story-21534539-detail/story.html|newspaper=Burton Mail|date=4 May 2011|accessdate=13 June 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150614093807/http://www.burtonmail.co.uk/Brewers-set-Legz-awards-night/story-21534539-detail/story.html|archivedate=2015年6月14日}}</ref> ，使他當選為球迷選出的最年度最佳球員第二名，僅次於[[亚当·莱格兹丁斯|亚当·莱格兹丁斯]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Maghoma thanks the fans|url=http://www.burtonmail.co.uk/Maghoma-thanks-fans/story-21534536-detail/story.html|newspaper=Burton Mail|date=6 May 2011|accessdate=13 June 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150614093858/http://www.burtonmail.co.uk/Maghoma-thanks-fans/story-21534536-detail/story.html|archivedate=2015年6月14日}}</ref>。由於與球隊合約期快結束，使马霍马的未來去向變得不明朗<ref>{{cite news|title=Albion braced for Maghoma exit|url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11750/6953009/albion-braced-for-Maghoma-exit|publisher=Sky Sports|date=26 May 2011|accessdate=13 June 2015|archive-date=2016-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160415040939/http://www.skysports.com/football/news/11750/6953009/albion-braced-for-Maghoma-exit|dead-url=no}}</ref>，教練亦接受他離隊的事實<ref>{{cite news|title=Pesch expects Maghoma exit|url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11750/6997557/pesch-expects-Maghoma-exit|publisher=Sky Sports|date=20 June 2011|accessdate=13 June 2015|archive-date=2019-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191018060431/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11750/6997557/pesch-expects-Maghoma-exit|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而马霍马拒絕了外國球隊的邀請<ref>{{cite news|title=Jacques: Let's have a crack at the title|url=http://www.burtonmail.co.uk/Jacques-Lets-crack-title/story-21534621-detail/story.html|newspaper=Burton Mail|date=2 July 2011|accessdate=13 June 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150614085411/http://www.burtonmail.co.uk/Jacques-Lets-crack-title/story-21534621-detail/story.html|archivedate=2015年6月14日}}</ref>，與保顿艾尔宾續約兩年<ref>{{cite news|title=Jaques Maghoma signs new Burton Albion contract|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/13949866|publisher=BBC Sport|date=1 July 2011|accessdate=13 June 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Maghoma set for Burton stay|url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11750/7011253/Maghoma-set-for-burton-stay|publisher=Sky Sports|date=30 June 2011|accessdate=13 June 2015|archive-date=2019-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191001192737/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11750/7011253/Maghoma-set-for-burton-stay|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2011/12球季首場聯賽，马霍马由為停賽而無法上場<ref>{{cite news|title=Albion duo a major doubt for Shrews|url=http://www.burtonmail.co.uk/Albion-duo-major-doubt-Shrews/story-21534656-detail/story.html|newspaper=Burton Mail|date=12 August 2011|accessdate=13 June 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150614094647/http://www.burtonmail.co.uk/Albion-duo-major-doubt-Shrews/story-21534656-detail/story.html|archivedate=2015年6月14日}}</ref>。他在新賽季首次上場是聯賽盃第一輪作客[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|伯恩利]]，他在臨完場前打進一球使球隊追成平手，需以進入加時賽以決勝負，可是球隊最終以6-3出局<ref>{{cite news|title=Burnley 6–3 Burton Albion|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/14368550|publisher=BBC Sport|date=9 August 2011|accessdate=13 June 2015|archive-date=2014-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140414023827/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/14368550|dead-url=no}}</ref>。马霍马新球季首次聯賽上場是2011年8月13日以1-1打平谢斯伯利的比賽，首顆進球是2-0擊敗[[斯温登足球俱乐部|斯温登]]的賽事取得<ref>{{cite news|title=Burton Albion 2–0 Swindon Town|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/14864061|publisher=BBC Sport|date=17 September 2011|accessdate=13 June 2015}}</ref>。马霍马在對[[吉林汉姆足球俱乐部|吉林汉姆]]的賽事導致踝傷，使他需休養一星期<ref>{{cite news|title=Pesch signing SOS after triple blow|url=http://www.burtonmail.co.uk/Pesch-signing-SOS-triple-blow/story-21534692-detail/story.html|newspaper=Burton Mail|date=26 September 2011|accessdate=13 June 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150614082756/http://www.burtonmail.co.uk/Pesch-signing-SOS-triple-blow/story-21534692-detail/story.html|archivedate=2015年6月14日}}</ref>，後來的診斷顯示他需要做六個星期觀眾<ref>{{cite news|title=Maghoma suffers injury setback|url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11750/7235301/Maghoma-suffers-injury-setback|publisher=Sky Sports|date=11 October 2011|accessdate=13 June 2015|archive-date=2019-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191017233942/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11750/7235301/Maghoma-suffers-injury-setback|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年10月22日，他在2-1擊敗布里斯托尔流浪者的比賽重返賽場，以替補身份入替上場<ref>{{cite news|title=Burton Albion 2–1 Bristol Rovers|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/15319518|publisher=BBC Sport|date=22 October 2011|accessdate=13 June 2015}}</ref>。對[[罗瑟勒姆足球俱乐部|罗瑟勒姆]]的比賽他拉傷大腿肌肉<ref>{{cite news|title=Frustrated Zola looking to find ruthless streak|url=http://www.burtonmail.co.uk/Frustrated-Zola-looking-ruthless-streak/story-21534890-detail/story.html|newspaper=Burton Mail|date=24 February 2012|accessdate=13 June 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150614094200/http://www.burtonmail.co.uk/Frustrated-Zola-looking-ruthless-streak/story-21534890-detail/story.html|archivedate=2015年6月14日}}</ref>，需等到2012年3月17日對[[托奎联足球俱乐部|托奎联]]的比賽才復出<ref>{{cite news|title=Sharps lesson is another hammer blow for Pesch|url=http://www.burtonmail.co.uk/Sharps-lesson-hammer-blow-Pesch/story-21534894-detail/story.html|newspaper=Burton Mail|date=12 March 2012|accessdate=13 June 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150614083734/http://www.burtonmail.co.uk/Sharps-lesson-hammer-blow-Pesch/story-21534894-detail/story.html|archivedate=2015年6月14日}}</ref>。整個球季他在各項賽事上場38次並打進球5球。

马霍马在2012/13賽季表現十分出色，球季揭幕日6-2大勝[[AFC溫布頓|AFC溫布頓]]的比賽，他取得進球和助攻<ref>{{cite news|title=Burton Albion 6 – 2 AFC Wimbledon|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19252386|publisher=BBC Sport|date=20 August 2012|accessdate=13 June 2015|archive-date=2012-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120925081135/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19252386|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8月28日聯賽盃第二輪4-2擊敗[[莱斯特城足球俱乐部|莱斯特城]]的比賽，他同樣打進一球<ref>{{cite news|title=Leicester City 2 – 4 Burton Albion|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19340403|publisher=BBC Sport|date=28 August 2012|accessdate=13 June 2015|archive-date=2013-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131017054107/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19340403|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月15日4-0大勝[[牛津联足球俱乐部|牛津聯]]，他打進兩球和交出一助攻<ref>{{cite news|title=Burton Albion 4 – 0 Oxford United|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19527997|publisher=BBC Sport|date=14 September 2012|accessdate=13 June 2015|archive-date=2012-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120917233344/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19527997|dead-url=no}}</ref>。單在球季上半季，马霍马已在23場聯賽打進6球。之後他在對[[弗利特伍德镇足球俱乐部|弗利特伍德镇]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Fleetwood Town 0 – 4 Burton Albion|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/21448255|publisher=BBC Sport|date=16 February 2013|accessdate=13 June 2015|archive-date=2013-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130219083248/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/21448255|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[埃克塞特城足球俱乐部|埃克塞特城]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Burton Albion 4 – 2 Exeter City|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/21482966|publisher=BBC Sport|date=23 February 2013|accessdate=13 June 2015|archive-date=2013-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130225045633/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/21482966|dead-url=no}}</ref>和摩尔甘比的三場比賽打進了四球<ref>{{cite news|title=Burton Albion 3 – 2 Morecambe|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/21502199|publisher=BBC Sport|date=26 February 2013|accessdate=13 June 2015|archive-date=2013-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130301041405/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/21502199|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而他本人亦因此當選為二月份最佳球員<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.burtonalbionfc.co.uk/news/article/monthly-awards-715662.aspx|title=Clean sweep for Brewers in npower awards|publisher=Burton Albion F.C.|date=15 March 2013|accessdate=13 June 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150612190639/http://www.burtonalbionfc.co.uk/news/article/monthly-awards-715662.aspx|archivedate=2015-06-12|deadurl=no}}</ref>，此外他亦成為英乙年度最佳球員的侯選十人之<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.burtonalbionfc.co.uk/news/article/fl-Maghoma-738741.aspx|title=More plaudits for Maghoma|publisher=Burton Albion F.C.|date=28 March 2013|accessdate=13 June 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150612191000/http://www.burtonalbionfc.co.uk/news/article/fl-Maghoma-738741.aspx|archivedate=2015年6月12日|deadurl=yes|df=}}</ref>。2012/13球季結束之際，球隊已提前取得晉級附加賽一席，马霍马在餘下的聯賽對[[艾宁顿斯坦利足球俱乐部|艾宁顿斯坦利]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Accrington Stanley 3 – 3 Burton Albion|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/21921478|publisher=BBC Sport|date=1 April 2013|accessdate=13 June 2015|archive-date=2013-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130404014412/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/21921478|dead-url=no}}</ref> 和[[韦康比流浪者足球俱乐部|韦康比流浪者]]分別打進一球和兩球<ref>{{cite news|title=Burton Albion 2 – 0 Wycombe Wanderers|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/21999091|publisher=BBC Sport|date=9 April 2013|accessdate=13 June 2015|archive-date=2013-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130412232707/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/21999091|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在晉級附加賽對[[布拉德福德城足球俱乐部|布拉德福德城]]的比賽，保顿艾尔宾在首回合以3-2領先，其中一球由马霍马主射[[點球|點球]]；可是布拉德福德城最終以總比數5-4擊敗保顿艾尔宾<ref>{{cite news|title=Burton Albion 1 – 3 Bradford City|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/22328159|publisher=BBC Sport|date=5 May 2013|accessdate=13 June 2015|archive-date=2013-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130505202331/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/22328159|dead-url=no}}</ref>。马霍马在整個賽季各項賽事上場50次打進18球，並入選[[PFA年度最佳陣容|PFA英乙年度最佳陣容]]<ref name=PFAteam>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/22331030 |title=Gareth Bale wins PFA Player of Year and Young Player awards |publisher=BBC Sport |date=28 April 2013 |accessdate=1 September 2015 |archive-date=2016-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160116023742/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/22331030 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，為首位入選的保顿艾尔宾球員，此外亦當選為球員選出年度最佳球員<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.burtonalbionfc.co.uk/news/article/awards-802039.aspx|title=Bell heads winners at Player Awards|publisher=Burton Albion F.C.|date=1 May 2013|accessdate=13 June 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130502221259/http://www.burtonalbionfc.co.uk/news/article/awards-802039.aspx|archivedate=2013-05-02|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

马霍马與球隊合約在2012/13年到期，他本人亦收到球隊提供的新合約，此外傳出數家英冠球會有意簽下他<ref>{{cite news|title=Championship: Middlesbrough keen on Burton star Jacques Maghoma|url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11680/8699231/championship-middlesbrough-keen-on-burton-star-jacques-Maghoma|publisher=Sky Sports|date=8 May 2013|accessdate=13 June 2015|archive-date=2019-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190927232454/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11680/8699231/championship-middlesbrough-keen-on-burton-star-jacques-Maghoma|dead-url=no}}</ref>。马霍马留隊機會渺茫，教練[[加利·路维特|加利·路维特]]亦接受他離隊的事實<ref>{{cite news|title=Rowett braced for Maghoma exit|url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11095/8724092/rowett-braced-for-Maghoma-exit|publisher=Sky Sports|date=20 May 2013|accessdate=13 June 2015|archive-date=2019-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191011180529/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11095/8724092/rowett-braced-for-Maghoma-exit|dead-url=no}}</ref>。马霍马效力保顿艾尔宾期間成為球迷最受歡迎的球員之一，被球迷選入釀酒者最佳陣容<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.burtonalbionfc.co.uk/news/article/your-football-league-brewers-xi-has-been-confirmed-2471038.aspx|title=YOUR FOOTBALL LEAGUE BREWERS XI HAS BEEN CONFIRMED|publisher=Burton Albion F.C.|date=30 May 2013|accessdate=13 June 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150612194539/http://www.burtonalbionfc.co.uk/news/article/your-football-league-brewers-xi-has-been-confirmed-2471038.aspx|archivedate=2015-06-12|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.swfc.co.uk/team/player-profile/jacques-Maghoma/19|title=Jaques Maghoma Profile|publisher=Sheffield Wednesday F.C.|date=29 June 2013|accessdate=13 June 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150420021233/http://www.swfc.co.uk/team/player-profile/jacques-Maghoma/19|archivedate=2015-04-20|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

===謝周三===
2013年6月，马霍马與英冠球會[[谢周三足球俱乐部|谢周三]]簽約兩年<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23069042|title=Sheffield Wednesday sign Burton winger Jacques Maghoma|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=27 June 2013|archive-date=2013-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130701060512/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23069042|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

马霍马首次代表新球會上場是對剛降級的[[女王公园巡游者足球俱乐部|女王公园巡游者]]，在37分鐘入替[[乔·麦塔克|乔·麦塔克]]，以2-1戰敗完場<ref>{{cite news |title=Championship: QPR beat Sheffield Wednesday 2–1 at Loftus Road |url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/live/match/287676/report |work=Sky Sports |date=3 August 2013 |accessdate=13 June 2015 |archive-date=2014-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141210233308/http://www1.skysports.com/football/live/match/287676/report |dead-url=no }}</ref>。效力謝周三期間，马霍马的上場時間和進球不如在保頓艾爾賓般那麼多，他大部份上場都是替補上場，首顆進球要在2013年12月21日才打進，可是仍以2-1輸給[[伯恩茅斯足球俱乐部|伯恩茅斯]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Sheffield Wednesday 1 – 2 A.F.C. Bournemouth|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/25375972|publisher=BBC Sport|date=21 December 2013|accessdate=13 June 2015|archive-date=2013-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131225180657/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/25375972|dead-url=no}}</ref>。數星期後在足總盃第三輪，他再次打進一球使球隊以4-1擊敗[[马科斯菲尔德足球俱乐部|马科斯菲尔德]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Sheffield Wednesday 4 – 1 Macclesfield Town|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/25633444|publisher=BBC Sport|date=14 January 2014|accessdate=13 June 2015|archive-date=2014-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140309135320/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/25633444|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年2月22日對[[哈德斯菲尔德足球俱乐部|哈德斯菲尔德]]的比賽，他打進在新球會第二顆聯賽進球，以2-0獲勝。對[[威根竞技足球俱乐部|威根竞技]]的比賽時受傷使他錯過了十一場比賽<ref>{{cite news|title=Sheffield Wednesday: Maghoma doubt for proud Owls|url=http://www.thestar.co.uk/sport/sheff-weds/sheffield-wednesday-Maghoma-doubt-for-proud-owls-1-6498061|publisher=The Star|date=14 March 2014|accessdate=13 June 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150627133245/http://www.thestar.co.uk/sport/sheff-weds/sheffield-wednesday-maghoma-doubt-for-proud-owls-1-6498061|archive-date=2015-06-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，以及因病而錯過兩場賽事<ref>{{cite news|title=Sheffield Wednesday: Maghoma pressing for Owls spot|url=http://www.thestar.co.uk/sport/sheff-weds/sheffield-wednesday-Maghoma-pressing-for-owls-spot-1-6249768|publisher=The Star|date=18 November 2013|accessdate=13 June 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150627134955/http://www.thestar.co.uk/sport/sheff-weds/sheffield-wednesday-maghoma-pressing-for-owls-spot-1-6249768|archive-date=2015-06-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。马霍马傷癒後在球季最後一場聯賽上場，在80分鐘入替，最終以2-1輸給[[伊普斯维奇城足球俱乐部|伊普斯维奇城]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Ipswich Town 2 – 1 Sheffield Wednesday|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/27167526|publisher=BBC Sport|date=4 May 2014|accessdate=13 June 2015|archive-date=2014-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140505224815/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/27167526|dead-url=no}}</ref>。整個賽季他共上場30次打進3球。

2014/15球季首場比賽對[[布莱顿足球俱乐部|布莱顿]]，马霍马交出一助攻使球隊以1-0小勝<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.swfc.co.uk/news/article/report-brighton-hove-albion-0-1-sheffield-wednesday-1815584.aspx|title=Report: Brighton & Hove Albion 0–1 Sheffield Wednesday|publisher=swfc.co.uk|accessdate=14 August 2014|date=9 August 2014|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140814195122/http://www.swfc.co.uk/news/article/report-brighton-hove-albion-0-1-sheffield-wednesday-1815584.aspx|archivedate=2014-08-14|deadurl=no}}</ref>。之後在英聯盃第一輪3-0戰勝[[諾士郡足球會|諾士郡]]賽事中打進新球季首球<ref>{{cite news|title=Sheffield Wednesday 3 – 0 Notts County|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/28652680|publisher=BBC Sport|date=12 August 2014|accessdate=13 June 2015|archive-date=2014-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140814221030/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/28652680|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年2月14日對[[米尔沃尔足球俱乐部|米尔沃尔]]的賽事，他交出三助攻使球隊以3-1全取3分<ref>{{cite news|title=Millwall 1 – 3 Sheffield Wednesday|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/31498955|publisher=BBC Sport|date=24 February 2015|accessdate=13 June 2015|archive-date=2015-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150226153830/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/31498955|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

儘管马霍马有意與球會續約<ref>{{cite news |title=Sheffield Wednesday: Jacques targets new Owls deal |url=http://www.thestar.co.uk/sport/sheff-weds/sheffield-wednesday-jacques-targets-new-owls-deal-1-7010015 |newspaper=The Star |location=Sheffield |date=18 December 2014 |accessdate=13 June 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150616095225/http://www.thestar.co.uk/sport/sheff-weds/sheffield-wednesday-jacques-targets-new-owls-deal-1-7010015 |archive-date=2015-06-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，最終他仍是約滿被球會放棄釋出<ref>{{cite news |title=Sheffield Wednesday release 11 players including Lewis Buxton |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/32596487 |publisher=BBC Sport |date=5 May 2015 |accessdate=8 May 2015 |archive-date=2015-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150624071752/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/32596487 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===伯明翰===
2015年6月，马霍马與[[伯明翰足球會|伯明翰]]教練[[加利·路维特|加利·路维特]]再度共事，簽下兩年合約另加一年選擇權<ref>{{cite news |title=Jacques Maghoma: Midfielder signs for Birmingham City |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/33289362 |publisher=BBC Sport |date=26 June 2015 |accessdate=26 June 2015 |archive-date=2015-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150708040150/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/33289362 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，首次上場是聯賽盃對[[布里斯托尔流浪者足球俱乐部|布里斯托尔流浪者]]的比賽，马霍马與先開紀錄最終以2-1晉級至下一輪。他在伯明翰首個聯賽進球是作客以2-0擊敗[[米尔顿凯恩斯足球俱乐部|米尔顿凯恩斯]]的比賽<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/34024836 |title=MK Dons 0–2 Birmingham |publisher=BBC Sport |date=29 August 2015 |accessdate=30 August 2015 |archive-date=2015-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151108185053/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/34024836 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==國家隊生涯==
2010年5月，马霍马被徵召上[[剛果民主共和國國家足球隊|民主剛果]]成年隊參與在奧地利和瑞士舉行的賽事<ref>{{cite news |url=http://afrique.kongotimes.info/sport/football/les-leopards-de-la-rdc-en-stage-en-autriche-et-suisse.html |title=Préparation CAN 2012: Les Léopards de la RDC en stage en Autriche et Suisse |language=fr |trans-title=CAN 2012 preparation: DRC's Leopards training in Austria and Switzerland |first=Aimé |last=Katumba |newspaper=Kongo Times |date=19 May 2010 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100601085658/http://afrique.kongotimes.info/sport/football/les-leopards-de-la-rdc-en-stage-en-autriche-et-suisse.html |archivedate=2010-06-01|deadurl=yes }}</ref>。5月20日，马霍马入選民主剛果B隊對[[沙特阿拉伯國家男子足球隊|沙特阿拉伯]]B隊並首次為國上場並打進一球<ref>{{cite web |url=http://radiookapi.net/sport/2010/05/20/foot-amical-rdc-arabie-saoudite-2-1/ |title=Foot-Amical: RDC-Arabie saoudite, 2–1 |language=fr |trans-title=Football friendly: DRC – Saudi Arabia, 2–1 |publisher=Radio Okapi |location=DR Congo |date=20 May 2010 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100524055451/http://radiookapi.net/sport/2010/05/20/foot-amical-rdc-arabie-saoudite-2-1/ |archivedate=2010-05-24|deadurl=no }}</ref>。马霍马在翌日首次代表成年隊上場，對手同樣是沙特阿拉伯，他在下半場換入<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.national-football-teams.com/matches/report/11018/Dr_Congo_Saudi_Arabia.html |title=DR Congo vs. Saudi Arabia 2010-05-21 |website=National Football Teams |accessdate=1 September 2015 |archive-date=2020-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200220134823/https://www.national-football-teams.com/matches/report/11018/Dr_Congo_Saudi_Arabia.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，之前第二次為國上場要等到2015年3月不敵伊拉克的賽事<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.jeuneafrique.com/226293/societe/rdc-cavanda-mpoku-n-sakala-ikoko-les-nouvelles-t-tes-des-l-opards/ |title=RDC: Cavanda, Mpoku, N'Sakala, Ikoko... les nouvelles têtes des Léopards |language=fr |trans-title=DRC: Cavanda, Mpoku, N'Sakala, Ikoko... the Leopards' new faces |first=Alexis |last=Billebault |newspaper=Jeune Afrique |location=Paris |date=9 March 2015 |accessdate=1 September 2015 |archive-date=2019-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191013031814/https://www.jeuneafrique.com/226293/societe/rdc-cavanda-mpoku-n-sakala-ikoko-les-nouvelles-t-tes-des-l-opards/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.radiookapi.net/sport/2015/03/31/foot-amical-la-rdc-sincline-de-nouveau-face-a-lirak |title=Foot-Amical: la RDC s'incline de nouveau face à l'Irak |language=fr |trans-title=Football friendly: DRC go down again against Iraq |publisher=Radio Okapi |location=DR Congo |date=31 March 2015 |accessdate=1 September 2015 |archive-date=2019-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191021030458/https://www.radiookapi.net/sport/2015/03/31/foot-amical-la-rdc-sincline-de-nouveau-face-a-lirak |dead-url=no }}</ref>。马霍马首次代表國家參與正式比賽是[[2018年世界盃外圍賽_(非洲區)|2018年世界盃外圍賽]]作客3-2擊敗[[布隆迪國家足球隊|布隆迪]]，三天後主戰迎戰布隆迪的賽事亦有上場，最終以2-2戰平，使剛果得以晉級至小組賽<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.radiookapi.net/2015/11/12/actualite/sport/mondial-russie-2018-burundi-0-1-rdc |title=Mondial-Russie 2018: le Burundi tombe devant la RDC (2–3) |language=fr |trans-title=World Cup Russia 2018: Burundi go down to DRC (2–3) |publisher=Radio Okapi |location=DR Congo |date=12 November 2015 |accessdate=17 November 2015 |archive-date=2019-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191008021309/https://www.radiookapi.net/2015/11/12/actualite/sport/mondial-russie-2018-burundi-0-1-rdc |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.football365.fr/etranger/autres-championnats/cm-2018-rd-congo-burundi-2-2-1285184.shtml |title=CM 2018: RD Congo-Burundi (2–2) |language=fr |trans-title=2018 World Cup: DR Congo-Burundi (2–2) |website=Football365.fr |date=15 November 2015 |accessdate=17 November 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151118102033/http://www.football365.fr/etranger/autres-championnats/cm-2018-rd-congo-burundi-2-2-1285184.shtml |archive-date=2015-11-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

